# === 💎 Inspiro AI · Git Ignore（v4.3 最終穩定版）===
# 功能：防止金鑰洩漏、減少暫存上傳、確保 Railway / GitHub 部署順暢
# 適用環境：GitHub + Railway + Render + Vercel

# === 📦 Node.js 相依與暫存 ===
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
.cache_node/
.output/

# === 🔑 機密金鑰與環境設定（絕對不要上傳）===
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.cert
secrets/
keys/
private/

# === 🏗️ 編譯與暫存輸出 ===
dist/
build/
.cache/
.tmp/
out/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# === 🧠 Logs 與除錯檔 ===
*.log
logs/
debug.log
nohup.out
*.pid
trace.txt

# === 🖼️ 自動生成的圖片與暫存輸出 ===
/generated/
public/generated/
uploads/
tmp_images/
temp/
preview/

# === ⚙️ 部署平台設定檔（自動生成，勿上傳）===
railway.json
render.yaml
vercel.json
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
fly.toml

# === 💻 系統與編輯器雜項 ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.tmp

# === 🧪 測試相關 ===
jest/
__tests__/
__mocks__/
coverage/
test-results/

# === 🚫 不應上傳的壓縮或備份檔 ===
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
*.rar
*.7z
*.bak
*.old
backup/

